-- ACS Presents Proposal, Says It Has `Friendly Intentions' Toward Hochtief
-- B y   M i k e   G a v i n
-- 2010-10-04T08:18:28Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-04/acs-presents-proposal-says-it-has-friendly-intentions-toward-hochtief.html
Actividades de Construcción y
Servicios, SA said it presented its concept for the acquisition
of a majority stake in Hochtief AG to board members. The company
“reconfirms its friendly intentions towards Hochtief,” ACS
said in an e-mailed statement.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
